OL,5,GThis morning saw the on-air launch of
OL,6,Gthe new BBC Breakfast studio.
OL,8,FThis is the first time in over a
OL,9,Fdecade that the programme has
OL,10,Freceived such a significant
OL,11,Fpresentation overhaul.
OL,13,FThe programme remains based at Media
OL,14,FCity in Salford but its new home is
OL,15,Flarger than the space it occupied for
OL,16,Fthe last decade and which it shared
OL,17,Fwith BBC North West's regional news
OL,18,Fprogramme.
OL,20,FLate last week, the BBC issued a
OL,21,Fpress release with some information
OL,22,Fabout the changes:
OL,3,CBBC Breakfast launches new look
