OL,5,F"The new space features some of the
OL,6,Flatest broadcasting technology,
OL,7,Fincluding high-tech GFX, whilst
OL,8,Fkeeping the iconic red sofa at its
OL,9,Fheart. It is also larger than the
OL,10,Fprevious studio and features three
OL,11,Fmore cameras. The new state of the
OL,12,Fart screen technology will allow the
OL,13,FBBC Breakfast team to tell stories in
OL,14,Fa creative, bold and imaginative way,
OL,15,Fand enable collaborative sharing
OL,16,Facross sites."The Breakfast team will
OL,17,Fshare the new space with BBC Sport,
OL,18,Fwho will use it for the daily
OL,19,FSportsday programme, live bulletins
OL,20,Fthroughout the day as well as the
OL,21,FFootball News Show, the twice-weekly
OL,22,Fprogramme available on BBC iPlayer.
OL,3,CBBC Breakfast launches new look
