OL,5,F"The new studio is part of the BBC's
OL,6,Fstrategy to introduce new, versatile
OL,7,Fstudios that can be used by multiple
OL,8,Fteams throughout the day to provide
OL,9,Fthe best value for audiences. The
OL,10,Fspace is going to be used for more
OL,11,Fthan 20 hours a day, 365 days a year."
